description:
This market will resolve to “Yes” if the Binance 1 minute candle for SOL/USDT titled 2023/01/03 12:00 in the ET timezone (referring to 12:00 PM ET) has a final “Close” price of 11.01 or higher. Otherwise, this market will resolve to "No". 

The resolution source for this market is https://www.binance.com, specifically the SOL/USDT “Close” prices currently available at https://www.binance.com/en/trade/SOL_USDT?_from=markets&theme=dark&type=spot with “1m” and “Original” selected on the top bar. 

To see the “Close” prices, mouse over particular candles and look at the value after “Close:” at the top of the chart. 

The API url https://api.binance.com/api/v3/klines?symbol=SOLUSDT&interval=1m with relevant startDate and endDate parameters may be used in the event that the chart is unavailable. 

Please note, this market is about the price according to Binance SOL/USDT; information from other sources or spot markets have no bearing on this market's resolution.
